summary: You probably may not have known, but David Tennant (the voice of Spitelout and narrator of the audio books) had one last line...
body: You probably may not have known, but David Tennant (the voice of Spitelout and narrator of the audio books) had one last line for his character, Spitelout, in the 3rd film of the franchise, and it was a celebrated cheer during Hiccup and Astrid’s marriage “To the Chief and Chieftess!” great way to wrap things up after a great time voicing for the films and TV series of the HtTYD franchise!

summary: Just listened to the latest David Tennant Does A Podcast With... and it was so wonderful. I really enjoyed it. Whoopi Goldberg...
body: Just listened to the latest David Tennant Does A Podcast With… and it was so wonderful. I really enjoyed it. Whoopi Goldberg was a joy to listen to, she is a fantastic storyteller and David did a great job interviewing her. I am really enjoying this little side project of his.
